    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"http://giordano.scalzo.biz/2009/10/21/no-more-excuses-junit-testing-log-messages/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Log</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>private static Logger log = Logger.getLogger(LoggingObject.class);\nlog.info(\"I'm starting\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or <a href=\"http://ecmendenhall.github.io/blog/blog/2013/05/05/testing-console-output-with-junit-and-infinitest/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">System.setOut()</a> </p>\n\n<pre><code>private final PrintStream stdout = System.out;\nprivate final ByteArrayOutputStream output = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\nprivate TerminalView terminalview;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1968017,
      "reputation" : 1796,
      "user_id" : 1767722,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/Uu0Mt.jpg?s=256",
