    "body" : "<p>Ran into this as well. I'm using gradle to manage my tasks and I put this in at the end of by <code>build.gradle</code> file :</p>\n\n<pre><code>test {\n  testLogging.showStandardStreams = true\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Now I see <code>System.out.println(whateves)</code>.</p>\n"
