    "question_id" : 29488900,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I am using <code>gradle</code>. I had this problem with both <code>System.out</code> and <code>java.util.logging.Logger</code>. I edited the following part of my <code>build.gradle</code> file:</p>\n\n<pre><code>test {\n  testLogging {\n    exceptionFormat = 'full'\n    events = [\"passed\", \"failed\", \"skipped\"]\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and added <code>showStandardStreams = true</code> under <code>testLogging</code>. The result was as follows:</p>\n\n<pre><code>test {\n  testLogging {\n    exceptionFormat = 'full'\n    events = [\"passed\", \"failed\", \"skipped\"]\n    showStandardStreams = true\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It fixed both of them.</p>\n"
  }, {
